Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:13.89,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.42,0:00:16.34,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是種滿白櫟樹的小路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:24.17,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,這些都是前往神殿的巡禮者們種的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:27.16,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,據說這個習俗是源於
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:30.09,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,西柯萊特曾遭遇重大災害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:33.00,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,有一位神官在此種植過白櫟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.14,0:00:39.04,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,現在神殿裡  希卡聖下在裡面居住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:41.54,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,希卡聖下？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:44.76,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,是一位被稱為「活著的傳說」的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:49.96,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,活著的傳說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.44,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,啊  能看見神殿了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:56.68,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:00:59.54,Kanojo text,,0,0,0,,泰勒騎士？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.14,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H42484B&\blur4\4c&H000000&}Save my world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:21.89,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H7E8086&\blur4}革命のゲーム
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:24.56,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H42484B&\bord0}差し出す一手が勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:25.48,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H42484B&\bord0}You ready？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.10,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H42484B&\bord0}準備はOK？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:45.16,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}迷宮なこの世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.16,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}蔓延る駒を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:49.71,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}If I could burn it all down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:52.84,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}出口は見つからない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.51,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}深く祈る想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:58.05,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}どこに消えていくの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.89,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&HFFFFFF&}Pray all night long
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.14,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&HFFFFFF&}聞こえてますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.39,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HEFF1EA&\bord0}Black & White
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:07.77,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}マス目の上で微笑む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:13.40,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}描くの最高のフィナーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:16.19,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}Survive my world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:19.20,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HEFF1EA&\bord0}革命のゲーム
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.82,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}差し出す一手が勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.99,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}才能で勝利を呼ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:26.70,kanojo op jp,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HEFF1EA&\bord0}Save my life
